    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "It isn't, we're now using an array of refinements by operator ( https://github.com/algolia/algoliasearch-helper-js/blob/d3bf223fcfe9da6a4a47c2349d758d402d67729a/dist/algoliasearch.helper.js#L8177 ) and all the other ones use the value to know which one to add/remove, so I wouldn't change the behaviour for this method only, but we could probably add a 4th parameter `override` ?\n",
